      "title": "My latest Guardian Books cartoon.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s640x960/a00abda48d6c3517b33bd9e3e71172097ab72501.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"880\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Image:  A small, angry boy stands in front of his parents. They are in modern clothes, but he is dressed as a regency gentleman with top hat, breeches, cane etc. He says &quot;No title, no estates, and less than a thousand a year! How am I ever to find a wife!&quot;  Caption:  Noah's parents realise that he has been drawn into the manorsphere.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s75x75_c1/a4f91b42ebbe186cd0a91a2304f335ff71fd8fea.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s100x200/55f3eeb3871fbcb307ea1cdcb0b492fc41672feb.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s250x400/ac0011926d5c607b52741bbc2eb257a3968d2031.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s400x600/9103cb2c9250957a864338673d92b5d420c9dbf5.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s500x750/0b92287e7f3ded4eb008fdf9275c66b387ce563f.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s540x810/2544dd456affee69e9b8a26654719fc33e7d24a8.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s640x960/a00abda48d6c3517b33bd9e3e71172097ab72501.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s1280x1920/527f7fe904201a5489125651f35d0e1c87bc7426.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/cb932b1c1e5cdd168707e4fc02558d3f/3cc1aac3fe48b7ab-13/s2048x3072/d0c13cc4d088c142da2902afe7214e8fc497cc5f.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
