      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/812982632363229184",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/812982632363229184",
      "title": "An Easter books cartoon for the Guardian ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s640x960/881c310327735b355d6bc94c739fcb66bb40857c.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"890\" data-orig-width=\"1600\" alt=\"Title: Easter Egg Hunt techniques inspired by great detectives   Panel 1: Sherlock Holmes. Deduce the exact location of every egg from seemingly unrelated details without leaving your room. Send your amazed sidekick to fetch them.   Panel 2: Jack Reacher  Hit the garden hard and fast.  Take no prisoners Get back on the road.  This approach results in a thrillingly intense hunt, but very few intact eggs.  Panel 3: George Smiley Meticulously assess documents, people and motives. Then scrupulously collect the eggs and dejectedly wonder if  any of it was worthwhile.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s75x75_c1/33655d8a1cd15790ba80d8f3da4ac9271cd0378a.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s100x200/2d8318221ecde444170c4809d28adf9435f1fb12.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s250x400/bd5eb3ce703cce72e9c1d5b4b83102f0c46509eb.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s400x600/fbb6ad0a361d3094d086411d3e7d463453dd611e.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s500x750/299a8a75fa86edfab06a662ead8ecda57cc94d13.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s540x810/92926ff7d8f229cdbd94fe064b75164999a32b7d.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s640x960/881c310327735b355d6bc94c739fcb66bb40857c.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/ccc8b0e2bbd58ca6-13/s1280x1920/70dcc9a83789abc4519854bac857f12d26cd177a.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d8ad118752ecf50413151553044fd543/c